                <li>
                    <span class="text-heading">CHILDREN'S PRIVACY POLICY</span>
                    <p class="pt-5">CHATalk takes special precautions to protect the privacy of our younger users. CHATalk does not knowingly collect personal information from children under the age of 13 (a “child”). The Service is not intended to be used by children under the age of 13.</p>
                    <p class="pt-5">If CHATalk learns that we have inadvertently collected personal information of a child without parental consent, we will take appropriate steps to delete this information. If you are a parent or guardian and discover that your child under the age of 13 has a registered account with our Service without your consent, please alert us immediately by emailing privacy@gamersx.gg so that we may delete that child’s personal information from our systems.</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span class="text-heading">YOUR CALIFORNIA PRIVACY RIGHTS</span>
                    <p class="pt-5">This section applies to you if you are a resident of the state of California (a “consumer”). California law requires us to disclose certain information regarding the categories of personal information we collect. For purposes of this section, Personal Information does not include information that is publicly available, that is deidentified or aggregated such that it is not capable of being associated with an identifiable consumer or device.</p>
                    <p class="pt-5">We collect Personal Information from and about you for a variety of purposes explained in this Privacy Policy.</p>
                    <p class="pt-5">We will collect data from the following categories of personal information:</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside pl-5 list-subpoint">
