                    <p class="pt-5"><b>Additional Opt-Out Choices:</b> Additionally, you may wish to opt out of the sale of your personal information (including Internet/network information, commercial information, and inferences) by third-party advertising networks, social media companies, and similar online advertising companies for targeted online advertising purposes. By visiting www.privacyrights.info or www.optout.privacyrights.info, you can opt out from sales of this type of personal information by businesses that participate in the opt out tool. To make opt-out requests related to mobile apps on your device for businesses participating in the DAA’s CCPA App-based Opt-Out Tool, you can download the appropriate app at www.youradchoices.com/appchoices.</p>
